               </li>
               <li class="flex items-center gap-4 group" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/resale-circular-economy.astro:evidence-li-3">
                 <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-blue-500 shadow-[0_0_10px_#3b82f6]" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/resale-circular-economy.astro:8ygl38"></div>
                 <span class="text-lg font-medium text-slate-200" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/resale-circular-economy.astro:evidence-txt-3">Second-Life Compliance</span>
               </li>
             </ul>
           </div>
           <div class="flex flex-col justify-center" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/resale-circular-economy.astro:evidence-text-wrap">
             <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/resale-circular-economy.astro:evidence-h3">Continuity without friction.</h3>
             <p class="text-slate-400 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-8" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/resale-circular-economy.astro:evidence-p">
               Circularity requires more than just recycling; it requires identity that travels with the item. TieBack ensures that product context remains useful over time, regardless of who owns it.
             </p>
             <div class="flex items-center gap-6" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/resale-circular-economy.astro:evidence-stats">
                <div data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/resale-circular-economy.astro:stat-1">
