        <h2 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-8 tracking-tight" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/resale-circular-economy.astro:e4yr28">Build trust that <span class="text-blue-600" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/resale-circular-economy.astro:9eb0t3">persists.</span></h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-slate-600 mb-12 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/resale-circular-economy.astro:8k9454">
          Ensure your products maintain their value and guidance across every transaction. Join the organizations building for a circular future on TieBack.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-6" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/resale-circular-economy.astro:8ygl38">
          <button class="w-full sm:w-auto px-12 py-5 bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white font-bold rounded-2xl transition-all duration-300 shadow-2xl shadow-blue-200 hover:-translate-y-1" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/resale-circular-economy.astro:y6o4u0">
            Request Early Access
