            <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M8 7h8a2 2 0 012 2v10a2 2 0 01-2 2H8a2 2 0 01-2-2V9a2 2 0 012-2z" /><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M16 3v4M8 3v4M3 11h18" /></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/resale-circular-economy.astro:stdoaj">Controlled Transfer</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600 mb-8 leading-relaxed" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/resale-circular-economy.astro:8k9457">Identity persists as products move. Ownership transfer workflows ensure a clean handover and continuity of the product record.</p>
          <ul class="space-y-4 text-slate-700 font-medium" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/resale-circular-economy.astro:card-list-1">
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/resale-circular-economy.astro:ddzuok"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg> Secure Handover</li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/resale-circular-economy.astro:ddzuoj"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg> Record Continuity</li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/resale-circular-economy.astro:ddzunx"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg> Status Transparency</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- Card 2 -->
        <div class="group relative bg-white p-10 rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 hover:border-blue-200 transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-2xl hover:shadow-blue-100/30 overflow-hidden" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/resale-circular-economy.astro:6g626y">
          <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-32 h-32 bg-blue-50/50 rounded-bl-full translate-x-16 -translate-y-16 group-hover:translate-x-12 group-hover:-translate-y-12 transition-transform" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/resale-circular-economy.astro:card-deco-2"></div>
          <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-blue-600 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-8 shadow-lg shadow-blue-200" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/resale-circular-economy.astro:6g626x">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 8v13m0-13V6a2 2 0 112 2h-2zm0 0V5a2 2 0 10-2 2h2z" /></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/resale-circular-economy.astro:stdoai">Branded Handover</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600 mb-8 leading-relaxed" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/resale-circular-economy.astro:8k9456">A chance to welcome the next owner. Provide a calm handover experience with care, maintenance, and guidance.</p>
          <ul class="space-y-4 text-slate-700 font-medium" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/resale-circular-economy.astro:card-list-2">
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/resale-circular-economy.astro:ddzunv"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg> Handover Packs</li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/resale-circular-economy.astro:ddzunu"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg> Care & Maintenance</li>
