        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/resale-circular-economy.astro:e4yr2a">La continuité au-delà de la première vente.</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-600 text-xl leading-relaxed" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/resale-circular-economy.astro:8k945t">TieBack structure le cycle de vie des produits afin que l&#x27;identité, le contexte et la confiance restent intacts à chaque transfert.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/resale-circular-economy.astro:6g627m">
        <!-- Card 1 -->
        <div class="group relative bg-white p-10 rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 hover:border-blue-200 transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-2xl hover:shadow-blue-100/30 overflow-hidden" data-ps="src/pages/use-cases/resale-circular-economy.astro:6g6270">
